I"‡<p>We are glad to share that we have been granted with IATA NDC Certification Level 4 as an aggregator due to our dual API and Agent Desktop capabilities including servicing, post-booking ancillaries selling and handling airline disruption notifications.</p>

<p><img src="/img/iata-ndc_certified_airgateway-gmbh-level4-export.png" alt="NDC certificate" /></p>

<p>Very special thanks to our deployment partners Farelogix Inc., ATPCO, and SITA for working closely with us on this relevant achievement.</p>

<p>We will continue growing our platform capabilities as well as the number of connected providers (airlines) currently counting +20 airlines.</p>

